data.description: Welcome to this charming, updated 3 bedroom, 1.5 bath home. The open concept boasts an updated kitchen with granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, a new farmhouse sink and an eat-in dining space. The spacious living area draws tons of natural light. The finished lower level with half bath allows for extra living space that includes an abundant storage area. Enjoy your spacious, fenced backyard for outdoor relaxation on the deck, with plenty of space for kids and fur-babies. Located across from an elementary school. Don't miss out on this gem!
